<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>HealthBridge | Solusi Kesehatan Digital</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

    <header class="hero-section text-center py-5 bg-primary text-white">
        <div class="container py-5">
            <h1 class="display-3 fw-bold mb-3">Solusi Kesehatan <br> Masyarakat Digital</h1>
            <p class="lead mb-5 px-md-5 opacity-75">Platform terintegrasi untuk melaporkan kondisi lingkungan, booking layanan kesehatan, dan memantau tren penyakit.</p>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3">
                <a href="/lapor" class="btn btn-light btn-lg px-5 py-3 fw-bold text-primary rounded-pill shadow">Buat Laporan</a>
                <a href="/booking" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg px-5 py-3 fw-bold rounded-pill">Booking Puskesmas</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section id="fitur" class="py-5 bg-white">
        <div class="container py-5">
            <div class="text-center mb-5">
                <h2 class="fw-bold">Layanan Utama HealthBridge</h2>
                <p class="text-muted">Kemudahan akses kesehatan dalam satu genggaman.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="row g-4 text-center">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4 rounded-4">
                        <div class="fs-1 text-primary mb-3"><i class="bi bi-calendar2-check"></i></div>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold">Booking Online</h4>
                        <p class="text-muted">Antre di puskesmas lebih mudah tanpa harus menunggu lama di lokasi.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4 rounded-4 bg-primary text-white">
                        <div class="fs-1 mb-3"><i class="bi bi-cloud-arrow-up"></i></div>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold text-white">Laporan S3</h4>
                        <p class="text-white-50">Unggah bukti foto kondisi lingkungan langsung ke cloud storage AWS.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4 rounded-4">
                        <div class="fs-1 text-success mb-3"><i class="bi bi-activity"></i></div>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold">Real-time Monitor</h4>
                        <p class="text-muted">Pantau grafik penyebaran penyakit di wilayahmu secara instan.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="py-5 bg-dark text-white text-center">
        <div class="container">
            <p class="mb-0">Nazwa Nur Salsa Bella (152023173) - Informatika Itenas</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>